        <actionDate>2021-01-28</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2021-02-24T21:16:37Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>COVID-19 Home Safety Act of </b><b><b>2021</b></b></p> <p>This bill requires the Consumer Product Safety Commission to report, and make available to the public, information about injuries and deaths from consumer products during the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) public health emergency. The report must be submitted every three months for the duration of the emergency.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
